readable.content: A child at a party swings a bat at a pinata , encouraged by a father . A little boy in an orange collared shirt is swinging a baseball bat . A little boy in a red shirt is swinging at a pinata . A little boy in orange hit the pinata as a man stands behind him . The small boy in an orange shirt gets some help from an adult while swinging at a pinata .
